parameters.finale:
A date denoting original airdate of series finale episode in
the UK.
parameters.winner: A character string denoting name of series winner.
parameters.avg_uk_viewers:
Average UK viewers in millions. Also see
ratings.
parameters.timeslot:
time of day that series' episodes aired in UK (24-hour
clock).
parameters.day_of_week:
A character string denoting weekday that series'
episodes aired in UK.

A character string denoting the name of one of the

parameters.runner_up_1:
A character string denoting the name of one of the
bakers who was a series runner-up. The number is not meaningful.
parameters.channel:
A character string denoting channel that series aired on:

parameters.premiere:
A date denoting original airdate of series premiere episode

title: Data about each series aired in the UK (raw)

Description
This dataset has one row per series aired in the UK as 'The Great British
